descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Cherry Video Chat, a fast-growing social app in 2020.

Within Cherry Video, you will find funny and exciting people around the world. Choose what you like and start a video chat in one tap. It’s up to you what you want to watch and who you want to know more about!

【Feature Highlights】
* Location and gender filters
* Tap to start video chatting
* Live Video Chat instantly to get more vibe
* Watch short videos of your favorites
* Send Instant messages
* Send gifts to your friends
* Safe and Secure, you don’t have to worry about exposing yourself to the internet.
* Friendship or relationship, it’s your choice
* Young social app

【Tips for Better Experience】
* Like & Say HI: Don't forget to like the one you like and Say HI to the one you like.
* You can preview others’ profile to know each other better before starting a nice chat
* If you want to have a quick chat with someone, just find someone in Discovery.
* Become our VIP Members to enjoy more Privileges than general users, such as unlimited Chat Message, Live Video & Voice Chat, Discovery all around the world, Exclusive VIP Badge...
* If you enjoy instant chat, instant video call, and voice call or talk live, share with lovely friends for fun!

【Privacy & User Data】
* Private and safe chats
* Video chats start only you accept
* Report or block users that are acting against our policy
* Please respect other users and follow our guidelines to keep Cherry clean.
* Your user data will always be protected on our secure servers and will not be shared with any third parties that are not mentioned on our privacy policy. Just always be careful about private information you may reveal while chatting on Cherry. Your location will never be fully disclosed.

Cherry is the best way to make new connections. Download now and get ready to connect to the world.
